query: Schedule a team meeting for next week and create a task list for the agenda.
response: To schedule a team meeting for next week, you can create an event in Google Calendar and invite all team members. In the event description, you can add a link to a Notion page where you've created a task list for the agenda. Additionally, you can share the Notion page link in the team's Slack channel for easy access.

metadata.description: Coordinate team activities across multiple tools
